\begin_layout Enumerate
Let's first consider what happens in the Cournot part of the game.
 We see that the NE of the Cournot part (note that it isn't a subgame) of
 the game is 
\begin_inset Formula $q_{1}^{*}=q_{2}^{*}=40$
\end_inset

